upgradeTo.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation.

upgradeToAndCall.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation and executes a function call.

constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the logic address, admin address, and initialization data.

receive.description: Receive function to accept Ether transfers.

admin.description: Returns the address of the current admin.

changeAdmin.description: Changes the admin of the contract.

implementation.description: Returns the address of the current implementation.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin of the contract is changed.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon of the contract is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the contract is upgraded to a new implementation.
